{
  "stem": "9558.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other one used to bring me some butter, the other one some fruit, which that was the best thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had something to eat, and I brought home something for-- for the family, they should have something to eat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that went on for three years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I got up 6:00, 6:30.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I came home 11:00, 11:30 at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, remember the teacher-- I never got the grade what I deserved because I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the guys what I used to make the homework for them, they got better grades.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Without my help, they would never pass a grade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had-- as I was older a little bit, we had problems with the guys, the Gentiles, because it was like-- --I think it was around-- I think it was half Jewish and half Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they felt that they had the majority and it's their country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And it was Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I belonged to the Zionist organization, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, sure, we got together every night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if I didn't-- the nights what I didn't have to go to school, because I think it was, if my memory is correct, it was three times a week.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we used to go-- 7:00 we got together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were there till about 10:00, 10:30.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We learned Hebrew, Jewish history.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we really had-- that was our social life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody was looking forward.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To get together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I went to a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was-- that was preparing to go to Israel to work, you know, like the halutzim in those days.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they took my older brother to the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
